                <p>Sections 56(1), (2) and (4) and 60 of the Communications Act 2003</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>93(8)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Sections 4 and 4A of the Communications Act 2003</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 94</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Procedure for granting of rights of use for numbering resources</p>
