              <td>
                <p>Article 109</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p> Emergency communications and the single European emergency number</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Sections 45 to 48 and section 51(1)(a) of the Communications Act 2003. Ofcom consulted on making amendments to the relevant general conditions which implement Article 109 in its December 2019 Consultation entitled: ‘Fair treatment and easier switching for</p>
                <p>broadband and mobile customers, Proposals to implement the new European Electronic Communications Code’ and will publish a statement confirming the changes</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
